snippet.title: Sonic Megamix Mania SHC2020 Teaser
snippet.description:
Welcome to the next level! Sonic Megamix Mania is back and better than ever baby! We're here at SHC 2020 with 3 action-packed zones full of fun. We also have a special guest that awaits for you at SHC only possible through the use of lock-on technology. Well, we've gotta hurry back to making this the best modding experience ever so see you at SHC!

CONTEST WEEK FROM: Monday 26th October to Sunday 1st November
https://www.sonichacking.org/entries/contest2020/274 
(Link will activate during contest week)
